name: Almondmilk Honey Flat White with Espresso

name: Blonde Roast

name: Caffè Americano

name: Caffè Latte

name: Caffe Misto

name: Caffè Mocha

name: Caffè Vanilla Frappuccino Blended Beverage

description: Caramel syrup meets coffee, milk and ice for a rendezvous in the blender, while whipped cream and buttery caramel sauce layer the love on top. To change things up, try it affogato-style with a hot espresso shot poured right over the top.

name: Caramel Macchiato

description: Buttery caramel syrup is blended with milk and ice, then topped with a layer of dark caramel sauce, whipped cream, caramel drizzle and a crunchy caramel-sugar topping—oh-so-beautifully delicious.

name: Caramel Ribbon Crunch Frappuccino Frappuccino
description: Buttery caramel syrup blended with coffee, milk and ice, then topped with a layer of dark caramel sauce, whipped cream, caramel drizzle and a crunchy caramel-sugar topping—oh-so-beautifully delicious.

name: Chai Crème Frappuccino Blended Beverage

name: Chai Latte

name: Chai Tea

name: Chocolate Cookie Crumble Crème Frappuccino

These layers ensure each sip is as good as the last; all the way to the end.

name: Cinnamon Dolce Crème

name: Coconutmilk Cascara Latte with Espresso

Each sip is as good as the last . . . all the way to the end.

In 2008 our master blenders and roasters created this for you—a smooth, well-rounded blend of Latin American coffees with subtly rich flavors of chocolate and toasted nuts, it’s served fresh every day at a Starbucks® store near you.

name: Pike Place Roast Decaf
description: From our first store in Seattle’s Pike Place Market to our coffeehouses around the world, customers requested a freshly brewed coffee they could enjoy throughout the day. In 2008 our master blenders and roasters created this for you—a smooth, well-rounded blend of Latin American coffees with subtly rich flavors of chocolate and toasted nuts, it’s served fresh every day at a Starbucks® store near you. (Decaf as you like it.)

name: Starbucks Cold Brew Coffee
